                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090920-124-defend1247 t18090920-124-punish728"></join>
               Transported for seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Baron Wood.</p>
